# 2D RVE: 100x100 mm box, periodic placement (the placer wraps disks across
# the box; the downstream generator is set non-periodic so disks crossing
# the boundary appear clipped).
# Disks via Fuller grading; in 2D mode `fraction` is interpreted as area fraction.
#@output packing.dat
#@box 2 0.1 0.1
#@periodicity 2 1 1
#@seed 42
#@maxiter 1000
#@grading dmin 0.005 dmax 0.012 fraction 0.30
